				<p>
					Are you hilarious? Witty? Mildly interesting to be around? If any of these apply to you, Blog is the place to be. We cover a variety of content, from the <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2016/11/23/turkeys-wont-go-away/">Harvard turkey</a> to <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2017/1/17/how-to-schmooze-profs/">how-to</a> <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2016/11/15/guide-to-ticketing/">guides</a> to potential <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2016/11/29/yardfest-warzone/">Yardfest</a> artists. Blog is one of the most well-read sections of The Crimson, and our posts have been picked up by national and international news outlets.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong><a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/section/flyby/">Flyby</a></strong> is the flagship blog of the Crimson and covers student life&mdash;we follow all things happening on campus, from the <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2016/11/20/what-you-missed-at-harvard-yale/">Game</a> to <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2016/12/8/tiffany-trump-hls/">celebrity</a> <a href="http://www.thecrimson.com/flyby/article/2016/12/7/major-key-alert-khaled/">sightings</a>, and allow you to write about what most interests you.
